name: Stargate Spacewalk
description:
Inspired by an obsession for Space and Space Exploration and films like 2001: A Space Odyssey, Interstellar, and Gravity, this piece was created.

The light streak elements are from a photo I took of buildings and from where I was standing, it looked like a sort of Hyperspace jump that reminded me of Sci-Fi films; from the colors to the way the lights seem to go somewhere.
